summary: A made to order mod for some new home additions!
descriptionHtml:
I made this mod to order and it looks prety good, as always i tried to stick with original decor and feel.
First... there is a basement for Markath\'s Vlindrel Hall. I made it small but open and added mannequins to the first room and and alchemy lab to the second smaller room.
Second... Riften\'s Honeyside got some items moved and a Enchanters table added under the stairs of the basement which is already in the game.
author: Gregor
